<section id="nations">
  <div class="section-inner">
    <div class="nations-intro">
      <div class="reveal">
        <div class="section-eyebrow">
          <span class="section-label">The Confederacy</span>
        </div>
        <h2 class="section-title">Haudenosaunee<br>Six Nations</h2>
      </div>
      <div class="reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <p class="section-body" style="margin-top:1rem">The Haudenosaunee Confederacy — the Great League of Peace — is one of the world's oldest democratic federations, predating the United States Constitution by centuries. The Great Law of Peace (Gayanashagowa) governs all six nations, establishing principles of justice, balance, and consensus that influenced modern democracy. We carry our own passports. We are sovereign.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nations-grid">

      <div class="nation-card featured reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <svg class="nation-icon" viewBox="0 0 40 40" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
