        </svg>
        <div class="nation-name">Onayotekaono</div>
        <div class="nation-mohawk">Oneida Nation</div>
        <p class="nation-desc">People of the Standing Stone. Allied with the Americans in the Revolution, creating one of the most complex chapters in Haudenosaunee history.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="nation-card reveal reveal-delay-3">
        <svg class="nation-icon" viewBox="0 0 40 40" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
