        <div class="nation-name">Onöndowa'ga:'</div>
        <div class="nation-mohawk">Seneca Nation</div>
        <p class="nation-desc">Keepers of the Western Door. The largest of the six nations, known as the Great Hill People. Guardians of the western boundary of Haudenosaunee territory.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="nation-card reveal reveal-delay-1">
        <svg class="nation-icon" viewBox="0 0 40 40" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
