            <rect x="24" y="14" width="8" height="8" fill="#C4622D"/>
            <rect x="4" y="24" width="8" height="8" fill="#E8DFF5"/>
            <rect x="14" y="24" width="8" height="8" fill="#6B4C8A"/>
            <rect x="24" y="24" width="8" height="8" fill="#E8DFF5"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="culture-title">Wampum & Beadwork</div>
        <p class="culture-text">Wampum belts — made from white and purple wampum beads — are not decoration. They are treaties, records, and sacred documents. The Two Row Wampum Belt represents peaceful coexistence: two nations traveling together on the same river, neither interfering with the other.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="culture-item reveal reveal-delay-2">
        <span class="culture-num">04</span>
